{"tid":677153,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【明日大婚】只係儀式！鍾欣潼賴弘國9月才正式註冊","createTime":"2018-05-25T03:14:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-25T10:47:35.000Z","uid":71166,"like":29,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"463fcbd7cfa15e612e9776a4df09b9f03b239602","tid":677153,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T03:14:42.000Z","msg":"鍾欣潼（阿嬌）同未婚夫賴弘國（Michael）拍拖未夠一年就認定對方為終身伴侶，雖然兩人低調籌備婚禮事宜，但最終亦被媒體披露二人定於美國時間「5.25」完婚。不過據報道，鍾欣潼與賴弘國屬意9月喺香港擺酒時再正式註冊，因此呢個婚禮只是一個儀式。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn-modia-com-hk.cdn.ampproject.org/i/cdn.modia.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/rongxinnmm-1068x601.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn-modia-com-hk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fcdn.modia.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F05%2Frongxinnmm-1068x601.jpg&h=fcfed270&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿嬌認愛賴弘國僅半年就宣佈閃婚。（網絡圖片）<br />\n據悉，阿嬌母親、妹妹、表姊亦已相繼抵達洛杉磯，阿嬌聯同好姊妹阿Sa（蔡卓妍）日前完成Twins巡演後也已飛抵當地。另有媒體爆出，婚禮將於當地25日中午喺洛杉磯一間有近百年歷史嘅五星級酒店「Millennium Biltmore Hotel Los Angeles」舉行，並於晚上喺酒店內舉行西式晚宴。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn-modia-com-hk.cdn.ampproject.org/i/cdn.modia.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/rongxinnmm-1068x601.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn-modia-com-hk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fcdn.modia.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F05%2Frongxinnmm-1068x601.jpg&h=fcfed270&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n賴弘國跪地向鍾欣潼求婚（影片截圖）<br />\n選定低V婚紗<br />\n<br />\n此外，好姊妹阿Sa和容祖兒之前許諾為阿嬌婚禮贊助婚紗，據知，阿嬌最終選定咗一款低V設計嘅性感婚紗，應該會喺婚禮上耀眼奪目。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鍾欣潼Instagram留言"},{"pid":"79304be896329c5473984aea0d4363377f7394c0","tid":677153,"uid":71166,"like":16,"dislike":13,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T03:17:12.000Z","msg":"恭喜gill gill<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你真係好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a535f595943fd37624dd4e63b596eda9a349664c","tid":677153,"uid":155818,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T03:18:14.000Z","msg":"希望你嫁到個好老公<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b722db6502c2eb9b7eb4cb0f398a4de853728c7","tid":677153,"uid":71166,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T03:18:58.000Z","msg":"幸福GILL<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0877e5972b59676e982c9f953cfc9f150135afe7","tid":677153,"uid":74262,"like":37,"dislike":3,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T03:20:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1624d643915d9f4ce4de20f73ebf1fa4bae9d937","tid":677153,"uid":1159,"like":35,"dislike":4,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T03:22:11.000Z","msg":"因在陳冠希淫照事件中稱其本人淫照乃移花接木偽造，但其後陳冠希發表聲明指該批淫照乃屬實，而被網民恥笑逾十年的阿嬌鍾欣潼"},{"pid":"a3f11542cd81df35af66864cfee0326578faacfe","tid":677153,"uid":71166,"like":28,"dislike":2,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T03:23:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/25/112311_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F25%2F112311_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ff2f00b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nGill Gill靚足廿年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"524d7715fe05bb4a3a1cc468eefc752e5326aa6c","tid":677153,"uid":127272,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"0877e5972b59676e982c9f953cfc9f150135afe7","tid":677153,"uid":74262,"like":37,"dislike":3,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T03:20:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T03:23:38.000Z","msg":"黑化過程"},{"pid":"896514df9a12e710f9df342c6d6b6e17f5753034","tid":677153,"uid":2772,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":